[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "今日のライブ、初めてだけどいい感じだったよね！\nお客さんも楽しんでたし、アタシも楽しかった！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00192",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そうね。突発のステージのわりには\n悪くなかったと思うわ。でも――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00193",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "客は、あんたの友達のレスナって奴と、\nあとはたったの二人だけだったじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00194",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "通行人の多い場所だったのに、立ち止まる客は少ない。\nほとんどの人は、私たちに興味すらないのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00195",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "まぁ、今回は突発ライブでしたし、\n拙者らはまだデビューしたばかりでござるから――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00196",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "そうだよ！　これから活動を続ければ、たくさんの人が\nアタシたちのことを知って、好きになってくれるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00197",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……あんたはノリで始めたから分からないかも\nしれないけど、アイドルはそんな簡単じゃないの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00198",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "……え？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00199",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "デビューがこれじゃあ、今後大した話題にもならずに\n他の有象無象のアイドルに埋もれて腐っていくだけ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00200",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そうでしょ？　鬼門。\nそれはあんたが一番よく分かってるんじゃないの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00201",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00202",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "私は世界一のアイドルになりたいの。\nだから、こんなとこで満足してられない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00203",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "世界一のアイドル……\nうん、アタシも一緒に頑張るよ！　だから――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00204",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "本当に？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00205",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "社長にスカウトされたからっていうノリでアイドルを\n始めた程度の奴が、私と一緒にやれるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00206",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "う……\nそれは、そう、かもしれないけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00207",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……はぁ。このユニットに未来はあるのかしら。\n社長はいったいどうしてこんな素人を――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00208",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ヨハナ、そこまでにするでござる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00209",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "確かに今日のステージは、スタートとしては決して\nいいものとは言えないかもしれませぬが――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00210",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ライブを見て、良かったと言ってくれた方がいました。\n見てくれた方には確かに、拙者らの歌が響いていました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00211",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "だから、もう少し拙者ら三人で頑張ってみませぬか？\nもうダメだと決まったわけじゃないのですから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00212",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00213",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "デビューライブ、お疲れさまでしたわ。\n……あら？　話の途中でして？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00214",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "社長殿！　いえ、大丈夫です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00215",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……社長。どういうことなのよ、今回のライブは？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00216",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "十分な練習時間もない。宣伝もしてない。\nこれじゃあ誰も見に来なくて当たり前じゃない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00217",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "しかしおかげで、底の景色を見ることができましたわ。\nであれば、あとは上がっていくだけ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00218",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "それに、そんなことをしている猶予はありませんのよ。\n……わたくしの計画には",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00219",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "社長の、計画？　いったいなんなのよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00220",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "それは今後のお楽しみですわ。\nということで、２ｎｄライブの日程を共有いたします",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00221",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "おお！？　社長殿、シゴデキというやつですな！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00222",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふふ。実は１ｓｔライブと共に押さえていましたの。\n次のライブは３日後、場所は本日と同じくここですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00223",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "同様に、３日ごとにこの会場は押さえています。\n同じ場所で定期的にライブを行うことが大切ですのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00224",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そういうアイドルがいる。そう認知されることが、\n何よりの宣伝なのですから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00225",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "では、シゴデキのわたくしは別の仕事がありますので。\n失礼いたしますわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00226",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "わあ、たくさんライブができるってこと！？\n一緒に頑張ろうね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00227",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……私、今日はもう帰るわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00228",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ヨハナ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00229",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]